{"tid":1844471,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"連登仔早2日笑完人地未食藥 今日就個個轉番晒軚","createTime":"2020-01-26T15:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T15:55:21.000Z","uid":233643,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4c31c9112c6cce4bb97873bc120639fb9153d716","tid":1844471,"uid":233643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T15:38:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1838284/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1838284/page/1</a><br />\n人地1月5號已經有po講緊大陸政府將新型病毒屈落野味度 將責任推落人民身上<br />\n又講美國專家指出病毒好有可能黎自實驗室<br />\n但一大堆傻鳩見陳雲就反<br />\n仲瘋傳大陸人食野味既圖同片 其實做緊on9仔間接幫中共維穩<br />\n到今日就開始轉晒軚 <br />\n所以話上連登真係唔好盡信班傻鳩講既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be9017c136732d08140c23e5654b9620b65d241","tid":1844471,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T15:43:40.000Z","msg":"得撚閒理條私怨柒頭咩 冇呢個post我都唔知佢講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9142145cc3fc904c6b587c2ad5bb3eec8cdbdef1","tid":1844471,"uid":233643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T15:43:45.000Z","msg":"2014年<br />\n陳雲: 中共對香港超限戰勝利後 大陸人將會當街打死香港男人 擄走香港女仔輪姦 而警察不會理會<br />\n眾人: on9仔 未食藥 青山走犯傻鳩<br />\n2019年<br />\n差佬+大陸武警+解放軍喬裝警當街打死香港男仔 捉女仔番差館輪姦/捉上大陸<br />\n然後 眾人繼續話陳雲係傻鳩未食藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f847383cb8256f1afc4bc0d270b8d8f6823a405","tid":1844471,"uid":233643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0be9017c136732d08140c23e5654b9620b65d241","tid":1844471,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T15:43:40.000Z","msg":"得撚閒理條私怨柒頭咩 冇呢個post我都唔知佢講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T15:44:32.000Z","msg":"所以你到今日咪都仲係咁on9囉<br />\n繼續當係食野味傳番黎<br />\n做大陸既免費五毛維穩狗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"559541940f51c759c4ef6ed0b5e973e87664c919","tid":1844471,"uid":279326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T15:47:03.000Z","msg":"陳雲隻狗又出來吠"},{"pid":"4ccef2024c2e7598fb2ff06b446020255c33ecf0","tid":1844471,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T15:50:13.000Z","msg":"咁你想大家點對陳雲<br />\n如果一開始跟住陳雲說話做, 個運動一早輸左, 建制派選舉大勝,<br />\n對美國顯示香港已經民意逆轉<br />\n<br />\n就係因為陳雲呢個人唔可信, 所以冇人理佢講既野,<br />\n佢間中講有道理既野, 都改變唔到佢係一個有問題既人, <br />\n對於一個有問題既人, 佢講既野, 仲要人去理佢?"},{"pid":"b58d0f81e7666cbcf2552c0bb913b3b3ccff5954","tid":1844471,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T15:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Screenshot_20200105-082600_Chrome_6dYmn_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FScreenshot_20200105-082600_Chrome_6dYmn_1200x0.jpg&h=505461dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳雲叫政府唔好做入境衛生監控 咁會侵犯人權 仲有沙士唔醫會自然好 你信咗未?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}